Hey everybody ! Welcome to my new prefab for css named Scavange mod for css. For play this mod you just have to placed all the items on you'r map :) easy no ?

<u>Help</u> :

- To grab a barrel you just have to drop you'r gun on the other.
- To win a point , drop the barrel on the back of the generator.
- Small green gourds are medkits , press "E" tu use once only.

Look at the first scavange map here [>click<](http://css.gamebanana.com/maps/172177 ">clic<")

Thx for download :)
